    Isolation issue - The original version of this (renamed as GLTransformationMatrix) uses FloatBuffer objects obtained from GL to store and operate on the matrices - doing so destroys the ability to isolate the model, because the loaders use this to generate and store biological unit and non-crystallographic transformations.
